You are a senior React architect and UI/UX expert.

I want you to build a complete professional NGO website from scratch using React.

Project Name:
AWERDCP – Association of Water & Environment for Research & Development and Consumer Protection

Arabic:
جمعية الماء والبيئة للبحث والتنمية وحماية المستهلك

French:
Association Eau et Environnement pour la Recherche et le Développement et la Protection du Consommateur

Location:
Dakhla-Oued Eddahab, Morocco

IMPORTANT:
This is a FRONTEND ONLY project.
No backend.
No database.
Static website for now.
But architecture must be scalable for future backend integration.

---------------------------------------------------

TECH STACK:

- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- React Router
- i18next (for multilingual)
- Framer Motion (subtle animations)
- Lucide React icons

---------------------------------------------------

LANGUAGES:

The website must support:

- English
- French
- Arabic (RTL fully supported)

Implement full i18n structure.
Arabic must be fully RTL optimized.

---------------------------------------------------

WEBSITE STRUCTURE:

1) Home Page
   - Modern hero section with mission statement
   - Call-to-action buttons
   - Animated statistics section
   - Featured activities
   - Partners logos
   - News preview
   - Strong NGO style footer

2) About Page
   - Who We Are
   - Vision
   - Mission
   - Objectives
   - President (Dr. Aicha SAAD)
   - Region info

3) Activities Page
   Include sections for:
   - Environmental awareness workshops
   - Water stress conferences
   - Recycling initiatives
   - Ecological schools program
   - Scientific seminars
   - International participation

4) News & Events Page

5) Gallery Page
   - Images grid
   - Videos section
   Media stored in:
   /assets/images
   /assets/videos

6) Partners Page

7) Contact Page
   - Contact form (frontend only)
   - Address
   - Social media icons
   - Embedded map placeholder

---------------------------------------------------

